===Etymology===
Sanskrit [[मण्डप]], [[मण्टप]] (''maṇḍapa, maṇṭapa'') "pavilion, mandapa", a non-native word perhaps from the same source as [[मठ]] (''maṭha'') "hut, hermit's cottage".   <!-- ; (Tamil?) -->

